name: Global X Growth Asset Allocation Covered Call ETF
longDescription: The fund investing in exchange traded funds that provide exposure to a globally diversified portfolio of equity and fixed income securities. To mitigate downside risk and generate premiums, GRCC will be exposed to a dynamic option writing program.
fulldescription: The fund investing in exchange traded funds that provide exposure to a globally diversified portfolio of equity and fixed income securities. To mitigate downside risk and generate premiums, GRCC will be exposed to a dynamic option writing program. GRCC seeks to provide a combination of a high level of income and moderate longterm capital growth
